article_metadata.description: Healthcare.gov has officially survived its first full month online. The world as we know it has not ended, but as the website itself stabilizes (or doesn't), confusion toward its broader implications has become increasingly evident – if not rampant. The political battle has quickly shifted from website functionality to a pricing comparison of "old" [...]
